      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty\u2014it is in absolute dream condition! I have pampered this car since day one, and it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or speck out of place, and it drives like a cloud. I'm so excited for someone new to get behind the wheel and love it as much as I have. Come check it out, you won't be disappointed!",
