    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a superlative AP2-generation roadster, featuring the high-revving F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC power plant. This vehicle remains in factory configuration, exhibiting perfect compression and a pristine engine bay. The longitudinal powertrain is mated to a crisp, close-ratio six-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis utilizes a high x-bone frame and independent double-wishbone suspension, maintaining original geometry and exceptional torsional rigidity. This collector-grade example retains all original VIN tags on body panels, featuring flawless paint depth and zero bushing degradation. A mechanically synchronized, turnkey machine for the discerning enthusiast seeking an unmodified, showroom-quality driving experience.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
